{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "Mergers and acquisitions are given an extra test in due diligence: cybersecurity. Buyers and investors are increasingly demanding demonstrable digital resilience – and this has everything to do with risks that would otherwise only become visible after an acquisition.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "Buyers do not want a digital time bomb: systems must be safe, incidents must be handled properly, chain risks must be controlled. Companies without certification or with vulnerabilities in their supplier network are at risk of:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "- the deal is canceled;\n- the value is adjusted;\n- or substantial guarantees are required.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "The European NIS2 directive sets requirements for thousands of companies and their chain. During acquisitions, buyers are increasingly looking to see whether the target company meets these requirements – or whether there will be a compliance issue.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "For those looking to prepare for sales or financing, the [NIS2 Quality Mark (QM)](https://nis2qualitymark.eu/) offers a scalable, practical alternative to more stringent standards. This way you as an organization demonstrate that you manage risks - also in the chain.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "Digital security is not only a compliance issue, but also a strategic choice. Anyone who has their digital hygiene in order will retain their value.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0010", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0010", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
{"id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0011", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig.](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker__c4-paragraph__0011", "source_slug": "bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker", "source_title": "Selling a company without a cyber certificate? Increasingly a deal breaker", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/bedrijf-verkopen-zonder-cybercertificaat-steeds-vaker-een-dealbreaker.html", "source_date": "2025-08-18", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30"}}
